title: BRIEF-PrairieSky Announces First Quarter 2018 Results
text:
April 23, 2018 / 8:11 PM / Updated 6 minutes ago BRIEF-PrairieSky Announces First Quarter 2018 Results Reuters Staff 
April 23 (Reuters) - PrairieSky Royalty Ltd: * QTRLY FUNDS FROM OPERATIONS OF $0.22 PER COMMON SHARE 
* QTRLY TOTAL REVENUE OF $67.9 MILLION COMPRISED OF ROYALTY PRODUCTION REVENUE OF $64.1 MILLION AND OTHER REVENUE OF $3.8 MILLION FOR Q1 
* WILL APPLY TO EXTEND ITS NCIB FOR AN ADDITIONAL ONE-YEAR PERIOD 
* UNDER RENEWED NCIB INTENDS TO REPURCHASE UP TO $50 MILLION OF COMMON SHARES OVER A 12-MONTH PERIOD Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
